		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="408" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼斜上插刀鞘，随后立即朝前突进，突进和终点处均造成<span fontSize="25" color="#bababa">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼平插刀鞘，产生真空场吸引玩家，随后圆形斩击，造成<span color="#bababa">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼平插刀鞘，产生真空场吸引玩家，随后挥刀造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害，之后在原地产生</span><span color="#99ffff">霜驰</span><span>幻影，</span><span color="#99ffff">霜驰</span><span>在更大范围外挥一圈造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼斜上插刀鞘，进行快速突进，突进和终点处均造成<span color="#7fffd7">60%</span><span>伤害，随后大概率接</span><span color="#7fffd7">机巧声风</span><span>技能，小概率接</span><span color="#7fffd7">孤风刀势</span><span>技能或</span><span color="#99ffff">霜驰刀势</span><span>技能。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="429" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼迅速瞬移，原地留下一个<span color="#7fffd7">孤风</span><span>幻影，</span><span color="#7fffd7">孤风</span><span>挥出一刀风刃，同时剑鬼继续劈砍3-4道风刃，风刃均造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1343" width="429" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼在进行<span color="#bfffee">纵-横-纵</span><span>的普通攻击时，</span><span color="#7fffd7">孤风</span><span>幻影会协同攻击，剑鬼造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害，</span><span color="#7fffd7">孤风</span><span>造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1567" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼迅速斜砍出一刀风刃，造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害，该技能不单放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="1567" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffdf">(振刀2技能)<span color="#ffffff">剑鬼后撤，迅速连续劈出1-5刀风刃，每个造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，该风刃可被反击。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
