		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="429" height="87" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼在近处挥刀，最多可以进行3段普攻，有两种不同的方式：横-斜-纵、纵-横-纵，每段造成<span fontSize="25" color="#bababa">50%</span><span>伤害</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="435" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当生命值低于75%时，剑鬼右手持<span color="#99ffe5">破风</span><span>，左手拿来一把</span><span color="#99ffff">碎霜</span><span>，朝地用尽全力猛击，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">80%</span><span>+</span><span color="#66ffcc">80%</span><span>伤害，</span><span color="#99ffff">冰伤</span><span>范围比</span><span color="#66ffcc">风伤</span><span>大，随后进入风魔阶段。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1343" width="428" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼在进行<span color="#bfeeff">横-斜-纵</span><span>的普通攻击时，</span><span color="#99ffff">霜驰</span><span>幻影会协同攻击，剑鬼造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害，</span><span color="#99ffff">霜驰</span><span>造成</span><span color="#99ffff">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#079c9c" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#079c9c">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼拼合枉死之面，随后朝前推行，造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">剑鬼放开枉死之面，面具追踪玩家，随后闭合发生爆炸，造成<span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔偶剑鬼.assets/Image_28.png')" x="719" y="585">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔偶剑鬼.assets/Image_29.png')" x="1391" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1119" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">受击后，剑鬼突然后撤，原地留下一个<span color="#99ffff">霜驰</span><span>幻影，剑鬼蓄力产生真空场吸引玩家，和</span><span color="#99ffff">霜驰</span><span>同时挥出一刀，剑鬼造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害，</span><span color="#99ffff">霜驰</span><span>造成</span><span color="#99ffff">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔偶剑鬼.assets/Image_30.png')" x="1391" y="1034">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔偶剑鬼.assets/Image_31.png')" x="64" y="352" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔偶剑鬼.assets/Image_32.png')" x="596" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔偶剑鬼.assets/Image_33.png')" x="576" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="739" y="1791" width="425" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当玩家距离剑鬼&gt;7m时，魔偶剑鬼就会开始格挡攻击。<br/><span color="#bfffdf">(振刀2技能)</span><span>剑鬼会格挡近战攻击。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1791" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">魔偶剑鬼会不定时的握紧左拳，作出一副「你倒是打啊」的架势。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
